::JetV/Crotale::
JetV arrives at the ship and begins to load his equipment on.  Unknown
to him another bot, Crotale enters the ship and stows away and an
empty weapon compartment.

"I will be by your side Pacifix" Crotale tells himself.  He then shuts
the door and locks it and piles some crates against it.
"Until the end..."

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "rAuq" <rauq@t...> wrote:
> --- Pacifix ---
>
> He sees Trailblazer, and smiles, "Good, get ready to go, and make
> sure that all of your stuff is in the ship, you don't want to forget
> anything now..." He warns. Turning back to Artemus, "Ok, pack
> your equipment, and follow Trailblazer. You're on the team. I'm
> Commander Pacifix, and I was given the task of chosing who
> comes on the mission or not. The Autobot Council isn't really
> discussing whether or not you get on the team, they were waiting
> for me to arrive, since there's a meeting I'm supposed to attend.
> Now, go with Trailblazer." He finishes, nods his head, and
> continues towards the Autobot Council's conference room.
>
